<indexterm zone="hb-coretext-font-create" role="1.7.2"><primary>hb_coretext_font_create</primary></indexterm>
<programlisting language="C"><link linkend="hb-font-t"><returnvalue>hb_font_t</returnvalue></link>&#160;*
hb_coretext_font_create (<parameter><link linkend="CTFontRef"><type>CTFontRef</type></link> ct_font</parameter>);</programlisting>
<para>Creates an <link linkend="hb-font-t"><type>hb_font_t</type></link> font object from the specified
